# research-triad — unified research CLI + skill stack

**PURPOSE:** 4 research primitives (arxiv + x-cli + gh search + WebFetch) become ONE composable surface. The wrapper IS the substrate.

**Doctrine:** see `references/TRIANGULATION-DOCTRINE.md`, `references/QUERY-PATTERNS.md`, `references/CITATION-FORMAT.md`, `references/DEGRADATION-PLAYBOOK.md`, `references/COMPOSES-WITH-CATALOG.md`, `references/PROJECT-TUNING-PROTOCOL.md`.

**🆕 First time using triad on a new project / new domain?** Read
`references/PROJECT-TUNING-PROTOCOL.md` FIRST. It is the difference between
load-bearing evidence and zero-result fan-fiction. Skipping the protocol on
project N+1 is the highest-EV mistake the triad surface allows.

